						<div class="postbody">I have a couple demos that run on the FDS on my homepage: <a href="http://www.disgruntleddesigner.com/chrisc/creations.html" class="postlink">http://www.disgruntleddesigner.com/chrisc/creations.html</a>  Source code is of course available in the archive.
